</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Erking<ex>er,</ex></expan> als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der wollen
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> der <expan>Hübn<ex>er</ex></expan> gekawft
                        süll <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol ver<expan>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>Hans<ex>en</ex></expan> Hübner für uns besant und
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>zu red</expan> geseczt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t,</expan> daz er von
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> wollen zu den
                            <expan>zeit<ex>en,</ex></expan> als im woll
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wurd, niht gewest hab, als er das mit
                                <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> wol <expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan> mug; im
                        hab <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> der burggraf, etwievil wollen geschikt an der
                        schult, die er im schuldig sey, als er denn vormals andre jar auch getan
                        hab. Dewcht ewch <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu dem
                            <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> icht zu <expan>sprech<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        hett, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        slewnigs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> von im <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg,</ex></expan> wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den,</expan> so <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim ist, on
                            <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> ad <expan>vinc<ex>u</ex>la<ex>m</ex></expan>.
                    </ab>
</div>
